::DarkMouse::

She squeezed his hand.  She loved him and would fight to the death 
for him.  she released his hand and stood on the right side of 
Megatron.  She had to protect her leader at all costs.  Even with her 
life.  Her programming made her that way.  But her spark put 
Scorponok in front of Megatron.  She turned and whispered at 
Megatron, "OK, now I'm nervious. If he turns that weapon on us, we're 
scrap." She sttod up straight and watched Panzertron.
